title: Duke Engineering ECE Master's Hooding Ceremony 2022

media:group.media:title: Duke Engineering ECE Master's Hooding Ceremony 2022
media:group.media:description:
A ceremony honoring and recognizing Duke's Class of 2022 Master of Science and Master of Engineering graduates in Electrical & Computer Engineering was held at 12 noon, Saturday, May 7 in the Reynolds Industries Theater on the campus of Duke University.
More: https://pratt.duke.edu/about/news/duke-engineering-celebrates-class-2022
